	<key>NSContactsUsageDescription</key>
	<string>To help you easily connect with people from your phonebook on Yambi, we need access to your contacts. By uploading your contacts to our servers, we can show you which people from your contacts are already on Yambi, making it easier for you to find them.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>We need access to your microphone to record audio for voice messages.</string>
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
	<string>We need access to your photo library to allow you to upload pictures to your profile.</string>
	<key>NSPrivacyUsageDescription</key>
	<string>We need access to your contacts in order to help you easily connect with people from your phonebook available on Yambi. Also, we need access to your microphone and your camera to help you upload files on our platform. Your personal information data (name, phone number, etc.) will be stored on our servers during your entire use of Yambi.</string>
